      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MCCLUGGAGE (2) recorded his 5th career win last time out (20.17) at this track and drawn box 2 for the first time here. Goes very well at the trip finding the frame in each of four starts. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. FRAGILE FRANKIE (1) jumped from a low draw and boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten a neck (20.19) behind MCCLUGGAGE at this track. Must be included in calculations. LESTER BANNER (4) could not have been more impressive a few runs back in his speedy 19.89 win at this track over 366m then has finished in the placings in both runs since. Should be in this for a long way. TWO FACED GWEN (7) cannot be left out after placing here at this trip last start.",
